  "# reptile\n\n## answer\n\nreptile\n[ˈreptaɪl]\nn. 爬行动物，爬虫类；卑鄙的人\nNot until the beginning of the 19th century did it become clear that reptiles and amphibians are in fact quite different animals.\n到了19世纪初，人们才清楚爬行动物和两栖类动物实际上是完全不同的两类动物。\n\n词根记忆：rept（爬）＋ile（表物，名词后缀）→爬行动物\n\nreptilian（a. 爬虫类的）\n\n\n\nWord List 37\n",
