  "# swamp\n\n## answer\n\nswamp\n[swɑːmp]\nn. 沼泽地，湿地（marsh）vt. 使陷入，淹没；使应接不暇，使疲于应对（overwhelm）\nSlogging through a swamp in the rain is not funny.<br>I have been swamped with other things.\n在大雨中穿过沼泽地可不是闹着玩的。<br>我一直忙着别的事。\n\n\n\nswampy（a. 沼泽的，湿地的）\n\n\n\nWord List 37\n",
